Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the beginning, there was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless, expanding existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空中的大哥大都是巨无霸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The biggest things in space are gargantuan beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,个个都是其星系门类里的巨子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each one is a heavyweight in its galactic division.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙是个难以想象的大地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe is an unimaginably large place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它大到人类确实难以领悟那种尺度的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's so big it's really hard for human beings...to actually comprehend things of these size scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球上和宇宙间 以大为美\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}On Earth and in the universe, size matters...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而它关乎不同的前途\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it matters in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空中 大不见得好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln space, bigger is not necessarily better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:01:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往往是优胜者生活奢侈 英年早逝\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And oftentimes, the winners live large and die young.
