Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[历史频道] 第二季 第十六集 宇宙巨物\N[History Channel] The UniverseⅡ 16of19 Biggest.Things.in.Space
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是宇宙间的珠峰\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They're the Mount Everests of the cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文学家们如狗仔队那样瞄着自己的望远镜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Astronomers aim their telescopes at them like paparazzi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渴望捕捉到它们每个动作的图像\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}eager to capture images of their every movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们是宇宙间的大哥大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They are the biggest things in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的规模简直难以置信\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and their sizes are truly mind-boggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于宇宙间的巨无霸来说 幸运的是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The good thing about being huge in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙比你还要巨大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is that the universe is even huger than you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 有足够的空间去延展\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so there's plenty of space to stretch out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将度量的尺度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and get your size measured...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给一探究竟的智能文明\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}among intelligent civilizations that are having a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在开始研究天文时 首先发现的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The first thing you find out...when you start studying astronomy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都乖乖真大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is how darn big everything is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你研究的几乎每一样东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Almost everything you're studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都远远超出人类的尺度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is so far beyond any kind of human scale...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我们日常生活中从未碰到过的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we're ever going to encounter in our normal lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙充满了庞然大物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe is brimming with gigantic objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们的太阳系里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Within our own solar system...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球是第五大行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Earth is the fifth biggest planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过它比起太空中最大的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it's a hundred million billion times smaller...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小上十亿亿倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than the largest stuff in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么谁又拥有宇宙间大哥大美誉呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So what holds the coveted title...as the biggest thing in the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多数天文学家认为是宇宙网络\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most astronomers agree it's the cosmic web...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系间超星系团的无边无际的鹰架\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an endless scaffolding of superclusters of galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四周是暗物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}surrounded by dark matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种无形而神秘的物质形态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an invisible and mysterious form of matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占有宇宙90%的物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that accounts for 90 percent of the universe's mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙间的大哥大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The largest thing in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:03:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你甚至会怀疑 它是否就是那回事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you might even wonder if it's a thing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是暗物质构成的网\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's a web of dark matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宇宙间滥竽充数\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that fills the volume of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗物质是我们无法看见的物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dark matter is this matter that we can't even see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不发出任何光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt doesn't emit any light...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 却遍布宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it is filled throughout the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是其中的结构\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and there's structure in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗物质是神秘兮兮的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dark matter is something much more mysterious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超乎多数人的了解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than most people know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 构成我的物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Literally, the stuff that makes me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗物质是毫不搭边的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}dark matter isn't made of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为你闻得出它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l don't think you could smell it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不认为你摸得到它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l don't think you could touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只有引力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt simply has gravitational attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗物质的宇宙网络要能够看得见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The cosmic web of dark matter becomes visible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前提是要有物体填补其中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when looking at the objects that fill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个宇宙网络确实就像是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This cosmic web really is almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三维的蜘蛛网\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a three-dimensional spider"s web.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在所有漩涡的中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At the very center of all the vortexes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都存在着超星系团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there are the superclusters...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数千个星系组成的星团\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}clusters of thousands of galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是星系间的丝网将它们连接起来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then filaments of galaxies connect them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盖了整个浩瀚的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all the way across the volume of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:04:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些网状结构的节点上的最深厚最强大的引力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The deepest, strongest gravity...at the intersections of these weblike structures...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是无处不在的气体瀑布\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is where all the gas falls...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就是星系以及星系团形成的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that's where galaxies form... clusters of galaxies form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是宇宙网络究竟有多大呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Butjust how big is the cosmic web?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果银河系如罂粟种子般大小\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf the Milky Way galaxy were the size of a poppy seed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么有形的宇宙 我们所看到的一切\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then the observable universe, everything we can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会玫瑰碗球场那般大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would be about the volume of the Rose Bowl stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 全部装进宇宙网络里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, that entire volume is filled with a cosmic web...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超星系团联系在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}superclusters linked together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从宇宙的一头到另一头\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from one side of the universe to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙网络的起源依然不明朗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The origins of the cosmic web remain uncertain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 科学家认为其最早的种子在大爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but scientists think its initial seeds were planted...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即宇宙的诞生时已经种下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the Big Bang, the beginning of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爆炸期间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}During the Big Bang explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个宇宙突然爆发 基本上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the whole universe blew up, essentially...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膨胀非常迅速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and expanded very rapidly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以宇宙的物质网络\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so the cosmic matterweb...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包含了大爆炸期间创造的所有原始物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}contains all of the original matter...that was created during the Big Bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产生了我们今日所见的极其庞大的结构\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just blown up into the very, very large structures...that we see today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家正致力于描绘出遍布整个宇宙的宇宙网络\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists are actively trying to map out the cosmic web...which spans the entire universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手段之一就是观察高温的X射线发光气体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One way is to look at hot, x-ray-emitting gas...
