Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从旋转的黑洞的南北两极喷出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the north and south poles of the spinning black hole.
