Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,位于3C236星系内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is located in the galaxy named 3C236...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在小狮星座内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is in the constellation Leo Minor.
