Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.81,0:23:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就像这喷枪最终耗尽了燃气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, just as this torch will eventually run out of gas...
