Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦黑洞耗尽其周围的物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When the black hole has consumed...all of the material in its immediate vicinity...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会什么都不会留给积吸盘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there'll be nothing left of the accretion disc...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沿着磁力线喷出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to get shot out along the magnetic field lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时喷射将告终结\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and thejet will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.20,0:23:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果黑洞就是这些巨大的射电瓣的始作俑者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf black holes are the producers...of these gigantic radio lobes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么宇宙间最大的黑洞又在哪里呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then what is the largest black hole in the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前科学家正在投注赢家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists are currently placing bets on the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提及宇宙间的大哥大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When it comes to the biggest things in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.69,0:24:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某些黑洞获得了记录本上的一席之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some black holes earn a place in the record books.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑洞是太空中的一个区域\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A black hole is a region of space...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里 引力超大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where the pull of gravity is so immense...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.61,0:24:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何东西都难逃其魔爪 光也不例外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that nothing can escape it, not even light.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.49,0:24:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无数黑怪兽遍布宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are billions upon billions of these black monsters...prowling the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.08,0:24:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们可以归类为两种规模\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They come in two size categories.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.54,0:24:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中多数属于恒星级黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most of them are the stellar mass black holes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.42,0:24:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,质量约是太阳的5到100倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which are about five to 100 times...the mass of our sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.43,0:24:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是超大质量黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then there are supermassive black holes...
