Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到的超大质量黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We have the supermassive black holes...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.15,0:24:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们在每个星系中心所见到的那种\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the kind that we seem to be finding...in the centers of every galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.28,0:24:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们有据可查的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where we've had the resources to look.
