Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.83,0:25:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑洞本质上并非大的区域\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Black holes are not physically large regions...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.21,0:25:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要是以质量来衡量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but when measuring their mass...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.80,0:25:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们就会成为星系间重量级的最大竞争者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they become top competitors...in the galactic heavyweight division.
