Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.80,0:25:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是我们太阳质量的300万倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that's about maybe three million times...the mass of our own sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.48,0:25:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 由于黑洞的密度非常之大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And yet, because black holes are so incredibly dense...
