Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.52,0:25:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而却有着异常强大的引力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but incredibly, incredibly powerful gravitationally.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.19,0:25:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顾名思义 这些黑怪兽\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As their name suggests, these black beasts...
