Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.37,0:25:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因就在于光都逃脱不了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because no light can escape them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.54,0:25:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以唯一能观察到它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So one can only be observed...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.25,0:25:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在其引力影响太空中的其它东西时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when its gravity affects something else in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.41,0:25:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸如路过的恒星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}such as a passing star...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.83,0:25:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者在它吞食周围的物质时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}orwhen it's gorging on matter around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.80,0:26:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么谁是当今黑洞的冠军呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So what is the reigning black hole champion?
