Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.15,0:27:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是我们地球质量的30万倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is over 300,000 times the mass of planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.24,0:27:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个宇宙灯塔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And this cosmic beacon...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.28,0:27:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们太阳系里的发电站\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is a literal powerhouse in our solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.75,0:27:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座天然气发电厂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This natural gas power plant...
