Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.53,0:36:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及其它化学物质也是紧紧地压缩的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and other chemicals very tightly compressed.
